# NETWORK::NETWORK_GET_MAX_NUM_PARTICIPANTS

## Summary
Returns the maximum number of players that can participate in this script (the number passed into NETWORK_SET_THIS_SCRIPT_IS_NETWORK_SCRIPT())

## Returns
* **INT**
